inbodydescription.para: @BeginDocumentation Name: cin - Standard input stream Synopsis: cin -> istream Description: cin corresponds to the C++ object with the same name. SeeAlso: cout, cerr
@BeginDocumentation Name: cout - Standard output stream Synopsis: cout -> ostream Description: cout corresponds to the C++ object with the same name. SeeAlso: cin, cerr
@BeginDocumentation Name: cerr - Standard error output stream Synopsis: cerr -> ostream Description: cerr corresponds to the C++ object with the same name. SeeAlso: cin, cout
